    The TaskInterface provides utility methods for all the tasks.

    Interface used for the remote method invocation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddFriendTask
    The class AddFriendTask implements the adding of friend by a user.
    GetFriendListTask
    The class GetFriendListTask implements the retrieval of the friend list by the user.
    GetScoreboardTask
    The class GetScoreboardTask implements the retrieval of the scoreboard by an user.
    GetScoreTask
    The class GetScoreTask implements the retrieval by a user of his score.
    LoginTask
    The class LoginTask implements the login of a user.
    LogoutTask
    The class LogoutTask implements the logout of a user.
    MatchTask
    The MatchTask class implements the match between two users.
    WQClient
    WQClient is the client program of WordQuizzle.
    WQClientGUI
    WQClientGUI is the client program of WordQuizzle provided with a GUI.
    WQDatabase
    As the class name suggests, this is the WQServer's database.
    WQServer
    WQServer is the core class of the Word Quizzle application.
    WQUser
    The WQUser class models a user and implements the comparable interface, sorting the users is necessary to build the scoreboard.
    WQWords
    The WQWord class implements the random retrieval of the specified number of words to be fed to two players during a match.

    Exception Description
